      Xerium Technologies, Inc. (NYSE: XRM), a leading global provider of 
      industrial consumable products and services, today announced that it 
      plans to release its financial results for the second quarter 2017 after 
      the close of regular market trading on Monday, July 31, 2017.
    

      The Company will hold a conference call following the release. The time 
      and access details are as follows:
    

